# Absolute origin of the Laravel API. The SPA (Vercel) and API (cPanel) live on
# different subdomains, so builds must point at the API host. Vite bakes this
# into the production bundle. (You can instead set VITE_API_URL in the Vercel
# dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables; a dashboard value wins.)
VITE_API_URL=https://api.demo.hms.vellixglobal.com
